On the customers, invoices, payments and refunds, and orders screens you have the option to download a spreadsheet that displays information from the list. 

It is possible to filter the information that appears on the spreadsheet by using the filters available in each of the above mentioned sections of the system. 

!cvsdownload.png!

To download a report, click on the CVS download link provided on the customers, invoices, payments and invoices, and orders lists. A spreadsheet will automatically be downloaded to your computer. Open the spreadsheet to view the report. 

!cvsspreadsheet.png!